    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with lots of love? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still running like a total champ. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super clean inside and out, and absolutely ready for its next big adventure with you! You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
