    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a 2017 Ford Focus RS, a masterclass in hot-hatch dynamics. This specimen features the 2.3L EcoBoost inline-four, utilizing a twin-scroll turbocharger to produce a robust 350 horsepower and 350 lb-ft of torque. The hallmark of this platform is the Ford Performance All-Wheel Drive system with Dynamic Torque Vectoring; the Rear Drive Unit (RDU) employs twin electronically controlled clutch packs to manage torque distribution across the rear axle, effectively neutralizing understeer. The 6-speed manual transmission remains tactile and precise, paired with a suspension setup featuring dual-mode adjustable dampers. Braking performance is anchored by Brembo four-piston monoblock front calipers and 13.8-inch ventilated rotors. This vehicle has been maintained with mechanical integrity at the forefront, including the critical head gasket update, ensuring the powertrain operates at peak thermal efficiency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
