    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great on the road! It's been well-loved and taken care of, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve priced it to sell because I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
